data.title: Richard L. Cheney - 51st Mayor Of Tampa
data.meta_description: Born: December 21, 1921Died: June 20, 1974Term: April 1, 1974 - June 19, 1974 (Acting Mayor)
data.text:
Born: December 21, 1921

Died: June 20, 1974

Term: April 1, 1974 - June 19, 1974 (Acting Mayor)

Richard Cheney served as President of City Council from October 3, 1967 through September 30, 1971 and again from October 1, through April 1, 1974 when he became acting mayor after Dick Greco resigned. He served in this capacity until his death on June 20, 1974.
